  "articleBody": "DHey everyone…


I’ve moved a lot of my assessments online this year. But something weird is happening 😅


Students are finishing 20-question quizzes in like 3–4 minutes 😳


When I check the logs, half of them didn’t even READ the questions properly.


Some even submit in under 2 minutes (?? how??).

Then after results they complain “Ma’am question tricky tha” 🤦‍♀️


