  "headline": "Why AI-Assisted Learning is Changing Classrooms Forever",
  "articleBody": "AI is no longer a future concept — it is becoming a core part of modern classrooms.


Here’s why educators should adopt AI-assisted tools:


• Personalized Learning

AI adjusts difficulty, pace, and explanation style for each learner.


• Reduced Manual Work

Question generation, feedback, and assessment creation take less time.


• Better Engagement

Interactive prompts and adaptive tasks keep learners motivated.


• Data-Driven Insights

AI highlights weak areas early, allowing targeted interventions.


AI isn’t replacing teachers — it’s empowering them to teach with more efficiency and precision.


What AI tools do you think will have the biggest impact in the next 3 years?",
